Package: microData
Title: World Bank and FAO Microdata Assistant
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Gutama Girja", "Urago", , "girjagutama@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5588-2301"))
Description: This package assists to read worldbank and FAO microdata files and 
    organize them with excel. The work flow starts with creating `new_workbook()`
    then loading `dictionary()` to write them to the workbook.
    `dictionary()` function tho extracts variable names and their description 
    from the web. Then, use `add_sheet()` to write the new table to an existing 
    excel work book. Finally, the `micro_csv()` function reads local data and 
    applies data attributes from the excel workbook.
